HEADWORD: Plashoot
<hw>Plash"oot</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A hedge or fence
formed of branches of trees interlaced, or <xex>plashed</xex>.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <rj><au>Carew.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
